data.description: Warm, Quiet, Close to Nature 10.5 Acres. 4 Bedrooms Plus, 2 Full Bathrooms, 1/2 Bathroom next to Laundry off Oak Cabinet, Solid-Surface Countertop, 4-5 Stool Island and Ceramic Tile Kitchen. Spacious, Bright Dining Area thru Sliding Glass Door to 16'x10' Deck. Master Suite, Adjoining Family and Living Rooms. Oak Hardwood Floors. Open Oak Foyer and Staircase to 2 Oversized Bedrooms w/ Sitting Areas, Full Bathroom and Additional Room with many possibilities....Office, Den, Playroom, Nursery. 1540 sq. ft. In-floor Heat Basement includes Lg Family, Bedroom and Storage Rooms. Paver Walkways lead to 3 Stall Woodstove Heated Garage, Nature Trails along the Deer River, thru the Woods and around the Apple trees.
